HIRAM: Hassle-free Instant Ride Access Management

A car rental system manage by Zanber where in they will provide the Cars available and user will just browse available cars and book.
Simple CRUD Operation 

Create - Add new car (Only Admin will be allowed to add new car since Zanber will be the one who will manage the system)
Read - Display Available Cars
Update - (Only Admin allowed to update car details)
Delete - (Only Admin allowed to delete cars)


1. List All Cars
Method: GET

URL: /api/cars/

Request Headers: None (if you removed authentication)

Sample Response:
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Toyota Vios",
    "brand": "Toyota",
    "model_year": 2022,
    "is_available": true,
    "daily_rate": 2000.00
  }
]
